HEADWORD: Aitchbone
<hw>Aitch"bone`</hw> <pr>(<?/)</pr>, <pos>n.</pos> <ety>[For
<ets>nachebone</ets>. For loss of <it>n</it>, cf. <er>Adder</er>. See
<er>Natch</er>.]</ety> <def>The bone of the rump; also, the cut of beef
surrounding this bone.</def> <altsp>[Spelt also
<asp>edgebone</asp>.]</altsp>⟦br⟧
[<source>1913 Webster</source>]</p>

